            <title>[CASSANDRA-8294] Wrong command description for nodetool disablehandoff</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-8294</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The description for the nodetool command &lt;b&gt;disablehandoff&lt;/b&gt; is wrong:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&quot;Disable gossip (effectively marking the node down)&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should be something like &quot;Stop sending hinted handoff&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Cassandra 2.1.1&lt;br/&gt;
Nodetool&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
